<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，快看！<delay frames="40" />
满天繁星中划过了一颗流星！<delay20 />
今晚的夜空真是别具一格啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">据说流星这东西，<delay8 />
其实是像砂粒一样细小的宇宙尘埃<delay8 />
燃烧起来形成的哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如此美丽的东西真面目竟然是尘埃，<delay20 />
实在是难以置信啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />流星！！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可恶～<delay8 />一眨眼就划过去了，<delay20 />
根本来不及许愿啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快看<delay8 />这道彩虹！<delay frames="40" />
如此美丽，以至于我都把刚刚那阴郁的天气<delay8 />
抛诸脑后了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噢，<delay8 />出彩虹啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然能看见这么吉利的东西，<delay8 />
总觉得赚到了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道彩虹的末端<delay8 />到底是什么样的啊。<delay frames="40" />
哪怕一次也好，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想近距离观察看看！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想不到竟然有机会<delay8 />看到双重彩虹！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经把刚刚那阴郁的天气<delay8 />
都抛诸脑后啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原本阴郁的天气来了个大转变，<delay20 />
真是让人大饱眼福啊！<delay frames="40" />
感觉是个好兆头。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这可真是让人大吃一惊啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是出彩虹就已经很少见了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天竟然一下子架起了两道来！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不觉得<delay8 />极光<delay20 />
就像是光芒形成的窗帘一样吗？<delay frames="40" />
给人一种触手可及的感觉。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是把它掀开来，不知道会是怎样的景色啊。<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />
那就会变回普通的夜空吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一副美不胜收的光景啊。<delay frames="40" />
望着如此美丽的极光，<delay20 />
就感觉浑身都充满了力量！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～！<delay20 />这极光可太漂亮啦。<delay frames="40" />
不枉费我<delay8 />在这寒风中跑外面来啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要是一大堆飞机<delay8 />在天上飞来飞去，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是要不了一会儿<delay8 />就变成阴天啦？！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀——！<delay20 />那我可受不了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">每次望着飞机云我都会有一个想法<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />要是能在天空中用云彩写下一段新年试笔，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不觉得会给新年
开个壮丽的好头吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飞机云还看得一清二楚啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
这下看来，<delay8 />
马上就要变天啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">说起来，<delay8 />
有人和你说过<delay8 />“今晚的月亮真美啊”这句话吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这句台词啊，<delay8 />
好像是前人想出来的告白语哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />跟我没什么关系就是啦！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们平常看到的<delay20 />
都是月亮的正面哦！<delay frames="40" />
你也没看过<delay8 />月球的背面吧？
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想像这轮明月一般，<delay8 />
成为一个表里如一的人啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一直抬头望着天空，<delay20 />
脖子就会特别酸痛<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但这轮满月<delay8 />实在叫人为之着迷啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>